Subject: [PATCH 3/3] scsi: qedf: do not touch __user pointer in qedf_dbg_fp_int_cmd_read() directly
Date:   Fri, 28 Jul 2023 08:58:19 +0200
Message-ID: <20230728065819.139694-4-oleksandr@redhat.com>
